data.description: Motivated Sellers. Final Price Drop. Wonderfully And Well Maintained 2018 Built Home 4 Bedroom Split Arrangements 2 Bathroom 2 Car Garage On A Nice Corner Lot With Covered Patio In Back Yard With Too Many Upgrades To Name. Enter Through The Open And Inviting Entry Area, Large Living Area Open To Chef's Kitchen With Island, Granite Countertops, And Plenty Of Cabinet Space, Carpet Only In A Few Rooms, Upgraded Lighting Package In Open Areas To Die For. The Community Has A Dog Park, Walking Trails, Two Fitness Centers, Several Play Grounds, A Spray Park, And Two Pools, And Walking Distance To Schools.  Bring Your Pickest Buyers. Call And Schedule An Appointment Today.
